#: ../../Network_APIs/TCP_Server_APIs.rst:684 b2a5f76b877b465980d6162e869921c4
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `pfree` method allows you to free a port. Like the `palloc` method, you "
"don't need to worry about the port allocation mode when using this method."
